          .content
            h1  The Mood Tree 
            p
              span.textLeft
                | The D&AD Awards celebrates outstanding work in the design industry. They wanted an installation, which would generate social activity on their twitter # and add to the atmosphere at the 2016 Festival.
              span.textRight
                | The Mood Tree analysed live tweets using twitter api and algorithms based on Stamfords Natural Language parser, which then changed the colour and text on each leaf, based on that tweets sentiment.
          .videoContainer
            .videoPlayer
              iframe#player1.yPlayer(src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/yVKqqdlHPLI?enablejsapi=1&loop=1&modestbranding=1&playlist=yVKqqdlHPLI&rel=0&showinfo=0', frameborder='0', allowfullscreen='', width='560', height='315')
