            .textContainer
              h1  Tassimo Leapmotion 
              p
                span.textLeft
                  | This installation was prototyped for Tassimo, the brief required the use of the newly released Leap Motion sensor, as a tool to navigate a product catalogue.
                span.textRight
                  | Featuring images, videos and online reviews, users could navigate the site using hand gestures. Programmed in javascript and with a Wordpress back end, this was a re-useable prototype that could used for other clients.
          .videoContainer
